---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main class="about-container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <span class="about-subtitle">Behind the Lens</span>
      <h1 class="about-title">The Philosophy</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left Side: Profile Photo / Intro -->
      <div class="about-profile">
        <div class="about-image-wrapper">
          <img 
            src="/src/assets/portraits/DSC00271_DxO.jpg" 
            alt="Portrait" 
            class="about-img"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="about-lead">
          Travel and street portraiture is an active, collaborative energy between
          the photographer, the subject, and the city. We want our customers to
          truly remember Tokyo when they look back on their photo session with us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Side: The Bio & Deep Dive -->
      <div class="about-content">
        <p>
          Tokyo Memory Co. was built to document the city and its visitors, not as
          a postcard, but as a giant landscape, filled with active participants.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our approach centers the focus on you, and your time here. At the
          end of every session, our photographer will instantly deliver every photo
          shot, via a QR code.

        </p>

        <div class="about-divider"></div>

        <h2 class="about-section-title">The Approach</h2>
        
        <ul class="about-features">
          <li>
            <strong>In-Camera Precision & Instant Delivery:</strong> 
            The magic happens on the street, not hours later at a desk.
            Our workflow focuses heavily on getting light and composition
            styling exactly right inside the camera the moment the shutter 
            clicks. Because the foundation is nailed in-camera, it unlocks a 
            streamlined pipeline that allows us to deliver your image gallery
            immediately after our session wraps.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Editorial Quality:</strong> Leveraging a technical background in micro-contrast optimization and meticulous color profiles, every frame is treated like a standalone magazine feature. 
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Human Interest:</strong> My long-form sessions are purely documentary. I blend into your day to create an uncompromising, authentic visual record of your experiences and movements across Japan's capital.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 6rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--muted, #71717a);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--serif-display, serif);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: inherit;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.25fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-image-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    background: rgba(125, 125, 125, 0.05);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted, #a1a1aa);
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .about-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(125, 125, 125, 0.15);
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .about-section-title {
    font-family: var(--serif-display, serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: inherit;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .about-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-features li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .about-features strong {
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* Responsive Adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .about-container {
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .about-header {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>